<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome | MyBot Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #2f3136;
            --text-main: #ffffff;
            --text-muted: #b9bbbe;
            --discord-blurple: #5865f2;
            --discord-hover: #4752c4;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #36393f 0%, #2f3136 100%);
            color: var(--text-main);
            margin: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero-container {
            max-width: 500px;
            padding: 40px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .login-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: var(--discord-blurple);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.3);
        }

        .login-btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--discord-hover);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.4);
        }

        .login-btn svg {
            margin-right: 12px;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
        }

        .footer-note {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            opacity: 0.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="hero-container">
        <h1>Mój Dashboard</h1>
        <p>Zaloguj się przez Discord, aby zarządzać swoimi serwerami i konfigurować ustawienia bota.</p>
        
        <a href="/login" class="login-btn">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 127.14 96.36" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M107.7,8.07A105.15,105.15,0,0,0,81.47,0a72.06,72.06,0,0,0-3.36,6.83A97.68,97.68,0,0,0,49,6.83,72.06,72.06,0,0,0,45.64,0,105.89,105.89,0,0,0,19.39,8.09C2.71,32.65-1.78,56.63.48,80.05a105.73,105.73,0,0,0,32.44,16.31,80.7,80.7,0,0,0,6.57-10.71,69,69,0,0,1-10.51-5c.82-.6,1.62-1.23,2.39-1.89a74.12,74.12,0,0,0,64.4,0c.77.66,1.57,1.29,2.39,1.89a69,69,0,0,1-10.51,5,80.7,80.7,0,0,0,6.57,10.71,105.73,105.73,0,0,0,32.44-16.31C129.58,51.25,125.05,27.51,107.7,8.07ZM42.45,65.69C36.18,65.69,31,60,31,53s5.09-12.73,11.41-12.73S54.08,46,53.86,53,48.77,65.69,42.45,65.69Zm42.24,0C78.41,65.69,73.25,60,73.25,53s5.09-12.73,11.44-12.73S96.11,46,95.89,53,90.8,65.69,84.69,65.69Z"/>
            </svg>
            Zaloguj się przez Discord
        </a>

        <div class="footer-note">
            Logując się, akceptujesz regulamin naszej aplikacji.
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
